---
// 仓鼠驱动管家 - Windows系统驱动管理工具
import Layout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = '首页';
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>仓鼠驱动管家 - 专业Windows驱动管理工具</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Layout title={title}>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
          <h1 class="hero-title">开源驱动管理，让电脑重获新生</h1>
          <p class="hero-description">仓鼠驱动管家是完全开源的驱动管理工具，为您提供一键式驱动检测、更新、备份和恢复功能。透明、安全、高效，是您电脑维护的得力助手。欢迎社区贡献和支持！</p>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="https://github.com/Gautown/HamsterDrivers/releases" class="btn btn-large">立即下载</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Gautown/HamsterDrivers" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">GitHub 仓库</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">智能扫描</h3>
            <p>快速识别系统中的过时、损坏或不兼容的驱动程序，提供详细的硬件信息报告。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">一键更新</h3>
            <p>自动匹配并安装最适合您硬件的官方驱动程序，省时省力又安全。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">驱动备份</h3>
            <p>更新前自动备份现有驱动，遇到问题可随时回滚到之前的稳定状态。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">驱动库</h3>
            <p>海量驱动数据库，覆盖主流品牌硬件，离线安装无需担心网络问题。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">系统修复</h3>
            <p>解决因驱动问题导致的系统蓝屏、死机、设备异常等常见故障。</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">性能监控</h3>
            <p>实时监控驱动运行状态，提供性能优化建议，让电脑保持最佳运行状态。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Layout>
  </body>
</html>